{"tid":1618221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"太古街坊話你知唔需要開戰都贏到","createTime":"2019-10-04T04:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T05:02:10.000Z","uid":328471,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"15afc7fbc7dbca96858305d48ff06a73b8b84234","tid":1618221,"uid":328471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:55:04.000Z","msg":"如果你仍然覺得太古街坊大部分係中產和理非 無用<br />\n唔該你地班冷氣軍師<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">自己行出黎現場</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算琴日啲狗係放tg清場 我地都無怯過！<br />\n論士氣比班狗好得多多聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">贏左！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太古街坊證明左唔需要用到暴力都可以威到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你要佢地圍狗搶返個被捕 有無諗過咁做只會益左班狗 比機會佢地拉走更多手足？<br />\n街坊唔係傻架 <span style=\"color: red;\">用把口屌狗先係宣洩情緒又能自保嘅最好方法</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">話人平行時空嘅你地 有幾貼地？</span></span>你地係咪唔知啲狗拉人係唔理你咩動機？唔通你話想救人佢就唔拉你？<br />\n<br />\n另外 太古係佢地屋企 點解要撩交打先 <br />\n話佢地唔覺醒嘅 不如講下你想佢地覺醒完做咩啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">想佢地9衝打交？呢個係開花嘅目的咩？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地係要撚狗 唔好再戀戰得唔得</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以唔該各位連登巴打絲 鬧街坊前諗下大局 同代入第一身角度睇啦<br />\n琴日由7點開始就重狗 根本唔適宜開戰<br />\n<br />\n我地打緊長仗 武力唔夠 就要靠人數<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔同班毅進仔 有組織有計謀<br />\n唔好係咁叫人送頭啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817299184da233d63fe1740d6411572548d54a24","tid":1618221,"uid":328471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:55:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6132cb98cfbcfa98cbf40901c626f418ccf665ed","tid":1618221,"uid":328471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:55:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c050bc9d6555e12fc2661cf94769d06bf78a211","tid":1618221,"uid":328471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:01:49.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"801357314ebd5cf43f4caf55684349cbd0e92cce","tid":1618221,"uid":328471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:02:00.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"1e93583e904c228f7b0c08f33e0d335693fda513","tid":1618221,"uid":328471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:02:10.000Z","msg":"推3"}]}